query:
SELECT 
  id,
  title, 
  slug,
  CASE 
    WHEN content LIKE '%This is a placeholder for the full blog post content%' THEN 'PLACEHOLDER'
    ELSE 'REAL CONTENT'
  END as content_type,
  LENGTH(content) as content_length,
  createdAt
FROM blog_posts 
WHERE published = 1 
ORDER BY createdAt DESC;
